---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonial Widget for Agencies — SocialProof" description="Agencies: collect client testimonials once and show them on every client site. SocialProof is built for multi-client workflows — one account, unlimited embed locations." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/agencies">
<style>

    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .pain-section { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .pain-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; }
    .pain-section > p { text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
    .pain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
    .pain-card { border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; }
    .pain-card .pain-emoji { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .pain-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pain-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 60px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .usecase-strip { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .usecase-strip h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
    .tag { background: #ede9fe; color: #6c47ff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .steps-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .steps-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .steps-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: left; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.6; }
    .vs-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .vs-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .vs-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .vs-table th { text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; background: #f9f9f9; color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #333; }
    .vs-table td.vouch { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td.them { color: #dc2626; }
    .quote-section { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 auto 16px; max-width: 600px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 18px 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-cta { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #6c47ff; text-decoration: none; }
    footer { padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
  
</style>
<section class="hero">
    <h1>The testimonial tool agencies actually recommend to clients</h1>
    <p>Collect client praise once. Display it anywhere — on your agency site, your clients' sites, your proposals. SocialProof is built for multi-site workflows and doesn't require a developer for each deployment.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Start free — no credit card</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/blog/">See how it works</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pain-section">
    <h2>The agency testimonial problem</h2>
    <p>You deliver great results. Clients tell you. But capturing that praise — and putting it where it matters — is always an afterthought.</p>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-emoji">📧</div>
        <h3>It lives in email threads</h3>
        <p>Your best client feedback is buried in a reply from 6 months ago. You remember it was good. You can't find it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-emoji">🔒</div>
        <h3>Google reviews are locked to Google</h3>
        <p>You have 22 Google reviews. None of them appear on your site. Prospects have to leave your page to read them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-emoji">😬</div>
        <h3>Asking is awkward</h3>
        <p>Clients are busy. A LinkedIn recommendation request feels like a favor. A form feels impersonal. You don't ask at all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-emoji">🏗️</div>
        <h3>No dev, no embed</h3>
        <p>You want testimonials on the homepage. Dev is on a different client project. It never gets done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <h2>How SocialProof fixes it</h2>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🔗 One link, unlimited responses</h3>
        <p>Your collection link works the moment you sign up. Send it to clients via email, Slack, or project handoff. They click, they type, done.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>✅ You approve before it goes live</h3>
        <p>Every testimonial sits in a moderation queue until you approve. Control exactly what the world sees — nothing slips through.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🖥️ Embed anywhere, no developer</h3>
        <p>One script tag. Works on Webflow, Squarespace, WordPress, Framer, plain HTML. Anyone on your team can deploy it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🎨 Matches every client's brand</h3>
        <p>The widget adapts to your site's colors — or your client's. No third-party logos. No off-brand review badges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📍 Put them in the right place</h3>
        <p>Service page, case study page, proposal template, pricing section — drop the widget exactly where the decision happens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>💰 Priced for agencies, not enterprises</h3>
        <p>Free forever for 1 widget. Pro is $9/mo — less than one hour of your time. No per-seat, no per-client fees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="usecase-strip">
    <h3>Built for every type of agency</h3>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Digital marketing agencies</span>
      <span class="tag">Web design studios</span>
      <span class="tag">SEO agencies</span>
      <span class="tag">Paid media agencies</span>
      <span class="tag">Branding studios</span>
      <span class="tag">Social media agencies</span>
      <span class="tag">Video production</span>
      <span class="tag">PR firms</span>
      <span class="tag">Copywriting studios</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="steps-section">
    <div class="steps-inner">
      <h2>Set up in 3 steps</h2>
      <div class="steps-list">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Sign up — your collection link is instant</h3>
            <p>No forms to build, no survey tools to configure. Your link is ready on signup.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Send it at project close</h3>
            <p>Add it to your delivery email, your client portal, or your offboarding checklist. One link, every client.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Approve and embed</h3>
            <p>Approve the good ones, drop the script tag on your site. Your team can do it without a dev ticket.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="vs-section">
    <h2>SocialProof vs. other options</h2>
    <table class="vs-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Feature</th>
          <th>SocialProof</th>
          <th>Google Reviews / LinkedIn</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Testimonials on your own site</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Embedded widget</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Hosted elsewhere — link only</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Moderation &amp; approval</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Full control</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Platform controls</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Custom branding</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Matches your site</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Always shows their logo</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>No developer needed</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ One script tag</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Manual copy-paste, no live sync</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Pricing</td>
          <td class="vouch">Free / $9/mo Pro</td>
          <td class="them">Free but zero embed control</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-section">
    <blockquote>"I spent years copying client praise from emails and pasting it into Squarespace. Now I just send my SocialProof link at project close and the testimonials appear on my site automatically."</blockquote>
    <cite>— Founder, digital marketing agency</cite>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Start building your testimonial library</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Upgrade to Pro at $9/mo when you're ready.</p>
    <a class="btn-white" href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Create your free account →</a>
  </section>
</Base>
